{
  "text": "As in other standard-resolution climate GCMs (see for instance [CITATION_1] ), the seasonal forecasting system discussed here fails to represent the North Atlantic weather regimes properly.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "129422027"
